A docker php image ready to deploy your project
==============================================

PHPloy is a opensource product maintained by banago (<https://github.com/banago/PHPloy>). This docker image allow you to run phploy with docker. The container is based on alpine linux, this result in a small image.
The image is packaged with SFTP tools.


Available environment variable :
================================

You can use the same environment variable as phploy permit. For the instance

`PHPLOY_HOST`
`PHPLOY_PORT`
`PHPLOY_PASS`
`PHPLOY_PATH`
`PHPLOY_USER`
`PHPLOY_PRIVKEY`

Usage example
=============
docker run --rm -e PHPLOY_HOST=1.2.3.4 -e PHPLOY_USER=username -e PHPLOY_PASS=password -v /path/to/src:/app pockost/phploy --help

Notes
=====
Thank to Banago for PHPLoy ! <https://github.com/banago/PHPloy>
Alpine linux is a small linux distro <https://alpinelinux.org/>

